<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><B><FONT COLOR="Red">Current Events and Activities</FONT></B> </FONT></CENTER>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/Satellit.gif" BORDER=3 HEIGHT=314 WIDTH=411>
