<DOCNO>WT01-B18-14</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA026-000281-B012-72</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://msi20.zo.utexas.edu:80/hornspec.htm 192.138.168.29 19970113202249 text/html 7189
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
