<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Photo Album of MSI's 50 Year Celebration Open House</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 2.0z Beta">
</HEAD>

<BODY TEXT= black BACKGROUND="../../images/chalk.gif">


<H1 ALIGN="center">Photo Album of MSI's 50 Year Celebration Open
House</H1>

<HR>

<P>
For those who could not attend our Open House, we offer these
photographs to give you a flavor of the event. These pictures
appeared in the Port Aransas newspaper, <I>South Jetty</I>, on
May 30, 1996. Our thanks to <I><B>Murray Judson</B></I> for taking
the pictures. </P>
<HR>

<P>
