http://msi20.zo.utexas.edu:80/staff/benner.htm 192.138.168.29 19970113212531 text/html 3684
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 21:36:13 GMT
