<DOCHDR>
http://msi20.zo.utexas.edu:80/staff/buskey.htm 192.138.168.29 19970113212644 text/html 3745
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 21:37:36 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Nov-96 14:57:00 GMT
