<P ALIGN=CENTER><STRONG>You can also order a copy of <I>Cancer Cure</I> <BR>online at <A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/">www.amazon.com</A>, or by calling Schine On-Line Services directly at 1 (800) FIND CURE.</STRONG></P>







