<DOCOLDNO>IA026-000277-B023-345</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ef.org:80/reports/Intro/index.html 198.77.86.203 19970113172026 text/html 6208
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 13 Jan 1997 17:22:04 GMT
