<DOCHDR>
http://www.ef.org:80/grants/guidelines.html 198.77.86.203 19970113171542 text/html 5272
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 13 Jan 1997 17:17:41 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 5101
