<DT><IMG ALIGN=baseline WIDTH=16 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../grf/b2.gif"><STRONG>Union of Concerned Scientists, </STRONG>Cambridge, Massachusetts

<DD><EM>1994<IMG ALIGN=baseline WIDTH=16 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../grf/s2.gif">
Amount: $442,000<IMG ALIGN=baseline WIDTH=16 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../grf/s2.gif">
Duration: 3 Years</EM><BR>

