1995).<BR>
<P><A NAME="157" HREF="#r157">157.</a> Geller, H., et al., <I>Bridging the Gap: Initiatives to Achieve 
President Clinton's Climate Commitment</I>, p. 13 (Washington, D.C.: 
American Council for an Energy-Efficient Economy, April 22, 1994).<BR>
<P><A NAME="159" HREF="#r159">159.</a>This carbon dioxide reduction data uses a national average for 
