<DOCHDR>
http://www.ef.org:80/reports/IV/A2.html 198.77.86.203 19970113175948 text/html 3013
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 13 Jan 1997 18:01:53 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
Content-type: text/html
