<DOCHDR>
http://www.ef.org:80/reports/IV/A3.html 198.77.86.203 19970113180005 text/html 5089
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 13 Jan 1997 18:02:09 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
