<P><A NAME="344"  HREF="#r344">344.</a> Williams, S., and Bateman, B., <I>Power Plays: Profiles of America's 
Independent Renewable Electricity Developers</I>, p. 391 (Washington, 
D.C.: Investor Responsibility Research Center, 1995).<BR>
<P><A NAME="345"  HREF="#r345">345.</a> Fully 26 percent of SMUD customers are willing to pay a premium for PV 
power generated on their own rooftops. Seventy percent were willing to 
participate in a "green pricing" program in which they would pay more on 
their monthly utility bills so that SMUD could establish a "Clean Energy" 
program.<BR>
<P><A NAME="346"  HREF="#r346">346.</a> The Results Center, <I>Sacramento Municipal Utility District: Solar 
