<DOCHDR>
http://206.61.184.43:80/olsen/DEA/mckinney.html 206.61.184.43 19970122071635 text/html 24977
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 07:16:26 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-0deb)
Allow-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
