<BR>
<BR><DD>The Clerk is directed to withhold issuance of the mandate herein until seven days after disposition of any timely petition for rehearing.&nbsp;  <U>See</U> D.C. C<SMALL>IR.</SMALL> R<SMALL>ULE</SMALL> 41.
