<DOCHDR>
http://206.61.184.43:80/olsen/MEDICAL/azprop200.html 206.61.184.43 19970122072406 text/html 26437
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 07:23:59 GMT
