1988. Washington, DC: Drug Enforcement Agency; 1988.</H5>

<H5>2. Grinspoon L., Bakalar J. Marihuana, the Forbidden Medicine.
New Haven, Conn.: Yale University Press; 1993.</H5>

<H5>3. In the Matter of Marijuana Rescheduling Petition, Docket
86-22, Affidavit of Daniel Daneac, M.D. Washington, DC: Drug Enforcement
Agency; 1987.</H5>

<H5>4. Doblin R., Kleiman M.A.R. Marihuana as anti-emetic medicine:
a survey of oncologists' attitudes and experiences. J Clin Oncol,
1991;9:1275-1290. </H5>
<HR>

<H4>1876 JAMA, June 21, 1995 -- Vol. 273, No. 23</H4>
<HR>

